<lb n="0202b08"/><head type="no">No. 1240</head>
<lb n="0202b09"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="001"/><note n="0202010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">【原】享保年間刊豐山大學藏本，【甲】高山寺藏古寫本</note><jhead>阿吒薄&CB00211;付囑&CB00057;</jhead></juan>
<lb n="0202b10"/>
<lb n="0202b11"/><div1 type="dharani"><p type="dharani">南無阿吒薄&CB00211;摩俱吒耶　摩訶藥叉那耶
<lb n="0202b12"/>　摩醯首羅耶泮毘摩質多羅<note n="0202011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔耶〕－【甲】</note><app n="0202011"><lem>耶</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>泮　那吒鳩
<lb n="0202b13"/><note n="0202012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">伐＝代【甲】</note><app n="0202012"><lem>伐</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">代</rdg></app>羅泮呵呵呵<note n="0202013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">呵＋（呵）【甲】</note><app n="0202013"><lem>呵</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">呵呵</rdg></app>泮泮<note n="0202014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">泮＋（泮）【甲】</note><app n="0202014"><lem>泮</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">泮泮</rdg></app>唅<note place="inline">引</note>　曳吒曳吒
<lb n="0202b14"/>曳吒曳吒　尼藍婆耶乾馱婆耶毘舍闍耶
<lb n="0202b15"/><note n="0202015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">莎訶之二字甲本作夾註</note><note n="0202015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（莎訶）二字本文＝（莎訶）二字夾註【甲】</note><app n="0202015"><lem>莎訶</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho"><note place="inline">莎訶</note></rdg></app>南無薄伽梵跋折羅軍荼利耶泮　跋
<lb n="0202b16"/>折唎薄悉陀耶泮　薄伽跋帝阿吒婆拘耶泮　毘
<lb n="0202b17"/>沙門那泮波波吒吒耶耶泮泮　因陀羅藥叉賴
<lb n="0202b18"/>耶泮毘盧釋迦耶泮　毘盧博芻藥叉那泮婆羅
<lb n="0202b19"/>摩泮速速去去馺婆訶　摩訶藥叉馺婆訶伽伽
<lb n="0202b20"/>伽伽羅羅
<note n="0202016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">泮＝伴【乙】＊</note>
<app n="0202016"><lem>泮</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">伴</rdg></app><app type="＊" source="0202016"><lem>泮</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">伴</rdg></app><app type="＊" source="0202016"><lem>泮</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">伴</rdg></app>
<note n="0202017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">泮＝伴伴【甲】</note>
<app n="0202017"><lem>泮</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">伴伴</rdg></app>　摩尼跋陀羅泮那羅
<lb n="0202b21"/>延都泮　摩訶迦羅泮阿耨陀耶泮甌婆難陀泮
<lb n="0202b22"/>蘇耆羅耶泮　南單那泮黑布單那泮闍摩羅闍
<lb n="0202b23"/>耶泮　目真&CB00444;耶泮蘇盧鳩
<note n="0202018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">槃＝盤【甲】</note>
<app n="0202018"><lem>槃</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">盤</rdg></app>茶唅<note place="inline">引</note>泮善女功
<lb n="0202b24"/>德耶泮降<note n="0202019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">怨＋（耶）&M062485;【原】</note><sic n="0202019" corr="怨耶" resp="【原】">怨</sic><app type="＊" source="0202016"><lem>泮</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">伴</rdg></app><app type="＊" source="0202016"><lem>泮</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">伴</rdg></app>　<app type="＊" source="0202016"><lem>泮</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">伴</rdg></app><note n="0202020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">泮＝伴伴【甲】</note><app n="0202020"><lem>泮</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">伴伴</rdg></app>藥叉藥叉速
<lb n="0202b25"/>速速速馺婆呵摩訶藥叉藥叉速速速速馺婆
<lb n="0202b26"/>呵阿阿阿阿阿阿&CB00425;&CB00425;遮遮&CB00330;&CB00330;&CB00330;<note n="0202021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00330;＋（&CB00330;）【甲】</note><app n="0202021"><lem>&CB00330;</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&CB00330;&CB00330;</rdg></app>跋跋
<lb n="0202b27"/>羅羅跋折羅荷<note place="inline">長引</note>吒吒吒<note n="0202022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">吒＋（吒）【甲】</note><app n="0202022"><lem>吒</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">吒吒</rdg></app>曳泮吒馺婆呵
<lb n="0202b28"/>吞攝馺婆訶阿吒阿吒阿呵阿呵呵呵唅<note place="inline">引</note>泮
<lb n="0202b29"/>斫迦羅護帝跋折羅力力力力拔拔拔拔急急
<pb ed="T" id="T21.1240.0202c" n="0202c"/>
<lb n="0202c01"/>急急頻陀攝持師子王吼吼吼吼呵呵呵呵
<lb n="0202c02"/><app type="＊" source="0202016"><lem>泮</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">伴</rdg></app>吒阿吒薄&CB00211;曳莎呵</p>
<lb n="0202c03"/><p>此&CB00057;急惡。若不清淨請不輒誦。有欲心。我遣
<lb n="0202c04"/>鬼王把金輪破汝頭。法誦舍利。諸法從緣起。
<lb n="0202c05"/>如來說是因。彼法因緣盡。是大沙門說</p></div1>
</body></text></TEI.2>